data.description:
Must see this impeccably maintained beautiful North facing 3272 sqft, 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, spacious 2 car garage single-family two-story home located within the highly desirable neighborhood of Stonebrier, zoned in "A-Rated" McKitrick, Martinez and Steinbrenner HS school district along with a charter school, Sunlake Academy of Math and Science. 

Located behind the gates of Sweetgrass, this popular "Mendoza" plan features an open layout having separate family and living room with formal dining room, all open to a beautiful kitchen having nook area overseeing the lake. Main level has one bedroom and a full bath. The home comes with a Water Softener, Central filtration, Rain Gutters, and a full set of Corrugated Steel Hurricane Shutters.

The chef's kitchen boasts upgraded stainless steel appliances featuring smooth top range and double oven, beautiful staggered ample 42 in. Maple cabinets w/ crown molding, a pantry and plenty of counter space. A spacious storage space is provided under the stairs. 

Upstairs has split floor plan with a game/media room in between. The master suite features a separate office/library space, a large walk-in closet and a luxurious master bath with dual sinks, a wonderful garden tub, and a separate walk-in shower with glass door. Upstairs has three more spacious bedrooms with one common bathroom and a separate laundry room.

All the rooms get bright sunlight, and are generously sized. Upgraded lighting fixtures, ceiling fans and neutral interior paint tones throughout the house help to create the right mood. All bathrooms have bidet fixture and bathtubs.

This home showcases a fabulous outdoor living space with a large-screened lanai of ~550 sqft, making it perfect for entertaining family and friends! The home is surrounded by large yard space overseeing the large lake and is a perfect place to sit outdoors for morning coffee or evening drinks!

Stonebrier community is a gated community with low HOA fees and offers endless resort-style amenities such as a community tropical pool with splash pad, children's spray ground and waterslide, 24-hrs fitness center, sidewalks, kids playground, beautiful trails with conservation/water views, basketball court, soccer field and a cricket pitch/ground. 

Conveniently located close to shopping and outlet malls, restaurants, Veteran's Expressway, I-75 & I-275, making the commute to Tampa a breeze!

Property is listed by owner. House is not staged and photos are not professionally taken, so may not give true view of the house. Pl schedule a visit by texting the owner at 201 334 7335.
data.whatILove: Beautifully maintained and safe family friendly community, beautiful lake view, spacious rooms providing plenty of opportunities to organize as per individual's choice/interest, additional storage areas in both lower and upper floor.
